         <abstract>The J. Walter Thompson
		  Company (JWT), founded in 1864, is one of the largest advertising agencies in
		  the United States. Greg Bathon was an executive with JWT, serving in a numver
		  of positions abroad, particularly in India, before becoming President of JWT
		  USA. The Greg Bathon Papers span the years
		  1966-1970 and include biographical sketches, correspondence, financial reports
		  and printed materials that primarily document Bathon's tenure as the head of
		  the J. Walter Thompson Company's Bombay (India) office. </abstract>
         
